### 7. Hardcoded Port (OWASP A05: Security Misconfiguration)

**Line 18** — Port `3000` is hardcoded. This leaks deployment assumptions and prevents flexible configuration.

```js
// ❌ CURRENT
app.listen(3000, () => { ... });

// ✅ FIXED
const PORT = process.env.PORT || 3000;
app.listen(PORT, () => {
  console.log(`Server running on port ${PORT}`);
});
```

